panorama to cubemap
-> https://jaxry.github.io/panorama-to-cubemap/

nasa images
-> https://svs.gsfc.nasa.gov/4851

Cube map conventions
    "px.png",  // Positive X
    "nx.png",  // Negative X
    "py.png",  // Positive Y
    "ny.png",  // Negative Y
    "pz.png",  // Positive Z
    "nz.png"   // Negative Z

Horizontal Cross
 +----+----+----+----+
 |    | PY |    |    |
 +----+----+----+----+
 | NX | PZ | PX | NZ |
 +----+----+----+----+
 |    | NY |    |    |
 +----+----+----+----+
